{"tid":1407453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"班狗記憶仲差過金魚","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:40:30.000Z","uid":292299,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ccbdea39829ab9795d9249d841d8e92682d194","tid":1407453,"uid":292299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"香港97沉淪後的誓詞<br />\n<br />\n本人（姓名），謹以至誠作出宣言（或，謹向全能之主發誓），本人<span style=\"color: orange;\">會竭誠依法為香港特別行政區政府效力為警務人員，遵從、支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律，以不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人及忠誠、努力的態度行使職權，執行職務</span>，並且<span style=\"color: red;\">毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">合法命令</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班狗唔單止係毅進仔，原來連金魚都不如，記憶差到無朋友，連當年做學警嗰陣連誓詞講過乜都唔記得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，淨係記得<span style=\"color: red;\">毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切</span>，一個二個都知法犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係時候貼返依段嘢喺俾佢哋睇，等佢哋回憶下宣誓當年講過啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b15eb92574c8946a665eff1c87ce73705382df","tid":1407453,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:27:51.000Z","msg":"同作地討論哂尻氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693c4767beb70a966b46b6905cd9eff62e105c52","tid":1407453,"uid":143559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"畜牲識字嘅咩"},{"pid":"deb26d4ff5cf1de91c814dba15538d7c9a6effa4","tid":1407453,"uid":292299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"貼狗屋，貼連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fb1d75b6c794fa839af11579cd790f914b9a7a","tid":1407453,"uid":292299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da44a30f8ce9b4afe645d2ff0d6cc3c9155de81","tid":1407453,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply